### Cross-Repo Conventions

#### Branch Naming
- Feature: `feat/<team>/<description>`
- Bug fix: `fix/<team>/<description>`
- Chore: `chore/<description>`

#### Commit Messages
Follow [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/):
- `feat:` new feature
- `fix:` bug fix
- `chore:` maintenance
- `docs:` documentation
- `refactor:` code restructuring

#### Code Review
- All PRs require at least 1 approval
- Architecture changes require team lead review
- Cross-team changes require affected team notification

